In a saucepan, heat cream just to boiling point. Meanwhile, place chocolate, egg, sugar, salt and vanilla in blender and blend for 1 minute. Add hot cream. Blend for 1 minute. Pour into pots de cr√®me cups or demi tasse cups. Chill. Serve with fresh whipped cream. Variations: Omit the vanilla and use rum or any liqueur. Take a few mint leaves that are chopped up and place into the cream to infuse, then strain prior to use.